# Notion import (legacy)

You are working on the **legacy** Notion → SQLite import pipeline (`packages/notion-importer/`).

**Do not use full re-import** (`notion:import`, especially `--clean`) to update production graph data. Ongoing edits go directly to `data/marloth.sqlite` — see [`docs/features/marloth-db.md`](../../docs/features/marloth-db.md) and root [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md).

Read before changing import behavior:

- [`docs/features/notion-import.md`](../../docs/features/notion-import.md)
- [`docs/features/marloth-db.md`](../../docs/features/marloth-db.md) (mapping rules for export mining)

Configuration precedence: **CLI flags > environment > defaults**.
